history.subject: 无法运行make debug命令
history.content:
root模式下使用make debug会出现该错误如何解决：

# Error constructing proxy for :1.89:/org/gnome/Terminal/Factory0: The connection is closed
# Failed to use specified server: The connection is closed
# Falling back to default server.
# Error constructing proxy for org.gnome.Terminal:/org/gnome/Terminal/Factory0: The connection is closed
make: *** [Makefile:223: debug] Error 1

如果不在root模式下会出现：

qemu-system-i386: Initialization of device ide-hd failed: Could not reopen file: Permission denied
make: *** [Makefile:213: qemu] Error 1

history.subject: 无法运行make debug命令
history.content:
root模式下使用make debug会出现该错误如何解决：

# Error constructing proxy for :1.89:/org/gnome/Terminal/Factory0: The connection is closed
# Failed to use specified server: The connection is closed
# Falling back to default server.
# Error constructing proxy for org.gnome.Terminal:/org/gnome/Terminal/Factory0: The connection is closed
make: *** [Makefile:223: debug] Error 1

如果不在root模式下会出现：

qemu-system-i386: Initialization of device ide-hd failed: Could not reopen file: Permission denied
make: *** [Makefile:213: qemu] Error 1

到Makefile文件  查找make debug 命令下的配置文件 看配置是否和你要操作的命令是否一致
